data.description:
WELCOME TO YOUR PERSONAL CANVAS UNDER THE ENDLESS SUNSHINE OF FLORIDA.  PRESENTING AN OPPORTUNITY TO CURATE YOUR UNIQUE RESORT-STYLE LIVING.  AS YOU STEP INTO THIS SPACIOUS 4-BEDROOM, 4-BATHROOM SINGLE-LEVEL POOL HOME, YOU ARE PRESENTED WITH A BREATHTAKING BACKDROP OF SUN-DRENCHED PALM TREES,
TROPICAL FOLIAGE AND AN EXPANSIVE WATER VIEW TOWARDS THE 16TH TEE OF THE DISTINGUISHED GREG NORMAN 
SIGNATURE GOLF COURSE AT JUPITER COUNTRY CLUB.  LOCATED IN THE CITY RONOWED AS THE "PROFESSIONAL GOLF CAPITAL" BY GOLF DIGEST.  THIS COUNTRY CLUB HOME AWAITS YOUR PERSONAL TOUCH.  NESTLED PRIVATELY ON A CORNER LOT.  IT OFFERS AN EXCEPTIONAL CANVAS FOR THOSE WITH A DECORATOR'S EYE, READY TO BE TRANSFORMED INTO THE WINTER RETREAT OR PERMANENT RESIDENCE OF YOUR DREAMS.  THE HOME FEATURES A DEN, FAMILY ROOM AND DINING ROOM AND WALK-IN CLOSETS IN ALL FOUR BEDROOMS PROVIDING SPACE FOR YOUR PERSONAL CUSTOMIZATION. THE PRIVATE, SPACIOUS LANAI WITH A POOL, SPA AND LONG VIEWS OFFERS A TIMELESS RESORT FEEL READY TO BE TAILORED TO YOUR TASTE.  JUPITER COUNTRY CLUB BOASTS AMENITIES SUCH AS GOLF, TENNIS, A FITNESS CENTER/SPA AS WELL AS FINE AND CASUAL DINING OPTIONS.  AND THE BEST PART? THERE IS NO WAITING PERIOD FOR GOLF MEMBERSHIP.  IT IS ATTACHED TO THE HOME, ALLOWING YOU TO IMMERSE YOURSELF IN THE COUNTRY CLUB LIFESTYLE RIGHT AWAY.  THIS SOUTH FLORIDA PARADISE IS MORE THAN A HOME; IT'S AN OPPORTUNITY FOR YOU TO EXPRESS YOUR STYLE AND CUSTOMIZE YOUR NEW LIVING SPACE ON YOUR TERMS. WELCOME TO YOUR FUTURE UNDER THE FLORIDA SUN.
